                <div class="card mx-auto" style="width: 20rem;">
                    <img class="card-img-top" src="Img/transportation.jpg" alt="Card image cap">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Transportation</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Rather you're looking for a family car or a sports car to enjoy your vacation we have it and public transportation. Check out our rental vehicles!</p>
